::Rex/Firearm/Striker::

Rex hits the grenade with his arm as it flies toward him, the grenade 
exploding and Rex flying backwards. Flies into a tree, flying through it and 
landing against another one. He growls, using a branch for support as he gets 
to his feet, firing another missile at Predator.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm growls as Predator shoots at his friend. He fires at him with his arm 
cannon, his rifle firing at Choran.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker raises an arm to block the knife, clenching his teeth as the knife 
stabs into it. One of the plasma charges hit him in the chest, sending him 
stumbling backwards, the other two missing him by an inch. He continues to 
fire with his shoulder blasters, firing again with his rifle.
